            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour </strong>to a plate and a splash of <strong>milk </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>to another plate with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>,<strong> half </strong>the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and mix together (this will make your breadcrumbs golden!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1648027860915-x200.jpg",
