        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>drained cannellini beans </strong>to the pot with your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>, <strong>Henderson’s Relish</strong>,<strong> vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until thickened – these are your<strong> beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
